   Technology &amp; Health:
   Court Dismisses
   Suit Against Pfizer
   Over Heart Valve
   ----
   By Michael Waldholz
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
06/01/90
</DATE>
